Policy access and editing

Org-wide / board policies live in Governance (and Auth for RBAC); slice-only 
reference data lives in each slice.

All slices read board policy only through governance_v2 / auth_v2 contracts
as read-only data.

Admin policy editing goes through a Governance-admin path that uses the same 
loaders/schemas under the hood, but adds validation, dry-run/commit, and 
ledger logging.
